             was indicted for <rs id="t18081126-42-off215" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18081126-42-off215" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18081126-42-off215" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18081126-42-cd216" type="crimeDate">17th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18081126-42-off215 t18081126-42-cd216"></join>, a ham, value 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18081126-42-victim388" type="victimName">
                  Humphry 
                  Wood
               <interp inst="t18081126-42-victim388" type="surname" value="Wood"></interp>
